        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3421684093" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12568927868701878815">This was a quick/short read. I wish it had been longer! The ending felt too rushed. 😔 This had soooo many feels! 🥰Magic. Mystery. Romance. Heartbreak. I went into this without knowing anything about the story. It starts out pretty slow but gets better and better. I think it’s a perfect summertime read! ❤️📚</span>

